data.description: FABULOUS 3 bedroom, 2 full bath rancher in a well-establish neighborhood.  Master bedroom boasts a walk-in closet, on suite bathroom with double sinks and a large garden tub perfect for relaxing after a stressful day.  The extra large eat in kitchen has all the appliances you will need to prepare meals for your family, along with a built-in bar for quick breakfasts.  Kitchen leads to a large pantry and laundry room with front load washer and dryer that will convey.  There is a cozy gas fireplace (as is with no known defects) in the large family room.  This home is a must see and won't last long.  New roof 8/2019; Trane heat pump replaced approximately 10 years ago, Hot water heater replaced approximately 4 years ago.  New laminate flooring in family room, hallway and kitchen.
